name: dhdata-viz
body:
### Welcome to DHData Visualization Tools.

This is a place where we can develop useful JavaScript libraries and example for visualizing digital humanities data on the web.

### Authors and Contributors

The libraries and examples are being developed by @jgsmith in support of dhdata.org and a series of blog posts about visualizing and analyzing digital humanities data.
